https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_38_51.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_39_51.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_37_50.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_38_50.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_39_50.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_37_49.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_38_49.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_39_49.png); background-position: -234px -254px, 22px -254px, 278px -254px, -234px 2px, 22px 2px, 278px 2px, -234px 258px, 22px 258px, 278px 258px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\" data-mw=\"interface\" data-style=\"0\" data-width=\"300\" data-height=\"300\" data-zoom=\"2\" data-lat=\"3227\" data-lon=\"2464\" data-mapid=\"0\" data-plane=\"0\" data-overlays=\"[&quot;_19d68d1d1d8e82174f84f815e4bfdca44ecd2d5d&quot;]\" href=\"/w/Special:Map/0/2/-1/2464/3227\"></a></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Advanced data</th></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"8\">NPC ID</th><td colspan=\"12\">5371</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<div class=\"floatleft\"><a href=\"/w/File:Spirit_of_Scorpius_chathead.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Spirit of Scorpius chathead.png\" src=\"/images/Spirit_of_Scorpius_chathead.png?24bb4\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"128\" height=\"143\" data-file-width=\"128\" data-file-height=\"143\" /></a></div>\n<p>The <b>Spirit of Scorpius</b> is a <a href=\"/w/Zamorak\" title=\"Zamorak\">Zamorakian</a> ghost.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> After completion of <a href=\"/w/Observatory_Quest\" title=\"Observatory Quest\">Observatory Quest</a>, he will give the player an <a href=\"/w/Unholy_mould\" title=\"Unholy mould\">unholy mould</a> and bless <a href=\"/w/Unholy_symbol\" title=\"Unholy symbol\">unholy symbols</a>. He is found south-west of <a href=\"/w/Ardougne\" title=\"Ardougne\">Ardougne</a> by the <a href=\"/w/Grave_of_Scorpius\" title=\"Grave of Scorpius\">Grave of Scorpius</a>, due north of the <a href=\"/w/Observatory\" title=\"Observatory\">Observatory</a>. An unholy mould <b>must</b> be claimed from him before he will bless any unholy symbols. He will not give the player an unholy mould if there is one already in their inventory.\n</p><p>Scorpius is close to both the <a href=\"/w/Red_salamander_(Hunter)\" title=\"Red salamander (Hunter)\">red salamander</a> hunting area and the <a href=\"/w/Ourania_Cave\" title=\"Ourania Cave\">Ourania Cave</a>.\n</p><p>Whilst alive, Scorpius was an astronomer and had an apprentice named <a href=\"/w/Phyrrys\" title=\"Phyrrys\">Phyrrys</a>. It is said that he created the art, and that he has a constellation named after him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Scorpius was later persecuted for his craft and his knowledge and instruments were almost totally lost.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> The art eventually returned to the world, as discovered in the <a href=\"/w/Observatory_Quest\" title=\"Observatory Quest\">Observatory Quest</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en-GB\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Stock\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Stock</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Dialogue\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Dialogue</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Changes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Changes</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Gallery_(historical)\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gallery (historical)</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Stock\">Stock</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Spirit_of_Scorpius?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Stock\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Spirit_of_Scorpius?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Stock\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center; margin:0;\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Item</th><th data-sort-type=\"number\">Price<br />sold at</th>\n</tr><tr style=\"text-align:center\"><td><a href=\"/w/Unholy_mould\" title=\"Unholy mould\"><img alt=\"Unholy mould.png\" src=\"/images/Unholy_mould.png?fe40f\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"31\" height=\"28\" data-file-width=\"31\" data-file-height=\"28\" /></a></td><td style=\"text-align:left\"><a href=\"/w/Unholy_mould\" title=\"Unholy mould\">Unholy mould</a></td><td data-sort-value=\"0\"><small>Free</small></td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Dialogue\">Dialogue</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Spirit_of_Scorpius?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Dialogue\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Spirit_of_Scorpius?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Dialogue\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"messagebox hasdialogue plainlinks\" style=\"border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\">This article on an <a href=\"/w/NPC\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"NPC\">NPC</a> has an associated dialogue page.<br /><b><a href=\"/w/Transcript:Spirit_of_Scorpius\" title=\"Transcript:Spirit of Scorpius\">Click here</a></b> for a transcript of possible conversations with this NPC.\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Changes\">Changes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Spirit_of_Scorpius?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Spirit_of_Scorpius?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery_(historical)\">Gallery (historical)</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Spirit_of_Scorpius?section=4&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Gallery (historical)\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Spirit_of_Scorpius?action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Gallery (historical)\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"text-align: center\" cellpadding=\"15\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/File:Spirit_of_Scorpius_(historical).png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Spirit of Scorpius (historical).png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Spirit_of_Scorpius_%28historical%29.png/98px-Spirit_of_Scorpius_%28historical%29.png?4a59c\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"98\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Spirit_of_Scorpius_%28historical%29.png/147px-Spirit_of_Scorpius_%28historical%29.png?4a59c 1.5x, /images/thumb/Spirit_of_Scorpius_%28historical%29.png/196px-Spirit_of_Scorpius_%28historical%29.png?4a59c 2x\" data-file-width=\"965\" data-file-height=\"1475\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/File:Spirit_of_Scorpius.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Spirit of Scorpius.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Spirit_of_Scorpius.png/81px-Spirit_of_Scorpius.png?aaf11\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"81\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Spirit_of_Scorpius.png/122px-Spirit_of_Scorpius.png?aaf11 1.5x, /images/thumb/Spirit_of_Scorpius.png/162px-Spirit_of_Scorpius.png?aaf11 2x\" data-file-width=\"540\" data-file-height=\"996\" /></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/File:Spirit_of_Scorpius_chathead_(historical).png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Spirit of Scorpius chathead (historical).png\" src=\"/images/Spirit_of_Scorpius_chathead_%28historical%29.png?88704\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"106\" height=\"109\" data-file-width=\"106\" data-file-height=\"109\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/File:Spirit_of_Scorpius_chathead.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Spirit of Scorpius chathead.png\" src=\"/images/Spirit_of_Scorpius_chathead.png?24bb4\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"128\" height=\"143\" data-file-width=\"128\" data-file-height=\"143\" /></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>29 March 2004 –<br />22 January 2007\n</td>\n<td>22 January 2007 –<br />present\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Spirit_of_Scorpius?section=5&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Spirit_of_Scorpius?action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Though he is a <a href=\"/w/Ghost\" title=\"Ghost\">ghost</a>, the player does not need an <a href=\"/w/Amulet_of_ghostspeak\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Amulet of ghostspeak\">amulet of ghostspeak</a> to talk to him. When you do talk to him, the chatbox says, \"This powerful spirit seems capable of speaking to you even though you are not wearing an Amulet of Ghostspeak.\"</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Spirit_of_Scorpius?section=6&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Spirit_of_Scorpius?action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small hideQuotes\"><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/w/Astronomy_book\" title=\"Astronomy book\">Astronomy book</a>, <i>Old School RuneScape</i>. <span>\"Before long, Scorpius used his knowledge for predicting the future, and, in turn, he called upon the dark knowledge of Zamorakian worshippers to further his cause.\" </span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Jagex. Postbag 21 - \"<a href=\"/w/Transcript:Somethingorotherwotsit#Letter_5\" title=\"Transcript:Somethingorotherwotsit\">Transcript:Somethingorotherwotsit</a>\", Letter 5, by Reldo. <i>RuneScape</i> Postbags from the Hedge. </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/w/Astronomy_book\" title=\"Astronomy book\">Astronomy book</a>, <i>Old School RuneScape</i>. <span>\"The kings of that time worked to banish the Zamorakian followers in the area, hiding all reference to Scorpius's invention, due to its 'evil nature'.\" </span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Observatory Quest\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Observatory_Quest\" title=\"Template:Observatory Quest\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Observatory_Quest\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Observatory_Quest?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a href=\"/w/Observatory_Quest\" title=\"Observatory Quest\">Observatory Quest</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">NPCs</td><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-parent\" style=\"padding